---
title: Chicken Parm Style Schnitzel with Roast Potatoes and Green Beans
description: We've got a tasty selection of schnitzel in the menu inspired by global flavours perfectly paired with crispy chicken! This Chicken Parm Style Schnitzel isn't your regular chicken parmigiana as it's served with roast potatoes and a side of green beans.
